<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="7" pageNumber="18">sp. n.</taxonomicNameLabel>
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 7" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figure 7. Bithynia mazandaranensis sp. n. a, b shell c operculum d detail of the shell surface." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/20809" pageId="7" pageNumber="18">Figs 7a-d</figureCitation>
